dc_description_s: These data layers represent trails for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Portage_Trails_2018.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Portage_Green_Circle_Trail_2018', 'Portage_Plover_River_Ski_Trails_2018', and 'Portage_Snowmobile_Trails_2018'. [GreenCircle is a vector representation of the Green Circle bicycle/pedestrian trail in Stevens Point, Wisconsin. Most of the trail was mapped using a resource grade GPS. The remainder is traced from airphotos. Recommended use scale is no larger than 1:2400.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
